e una función que permite registrar un vehículo en la blockchain utilizando el contrato inteligente.\n","\n","Cada vehículo es representado como un NFT único identificado por su VIN."],"metadata":{"id":"qRfN1v5c2JWO"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["def registrar_vehiculo(vin, marca, modelo, anio):\n","\n","    # Verificar conexión\n","    if not w3.is_connected():\n","        print(\"❌ Error de conexión con la red\")\n","        return\n","\n","    print(f\"🚀 Registrando vehículo: {vin}\")\n","\n","    try:\n","        # 🔥 Nonce correcto (incluye transacciones pendientes)\n","        nonce = w3.eth.get_transaction_count(account.address, \"pending\")\n","\n","        # Gas dinámico\n","        gas_price = int(w3.eth.gas_price * 1.2)\n","\n","        # Construcción de la transacción\n","        txn = contract.functions.registerVehicle(\n","            account.address,  # dueño del NFT\n","            vin,\n","            marca,\n","            modelo,\n","            anio\n","        ).build_transaction({\n","            \"chainId\": 11155111,  # Red Sepolia\n","            \"from\": account.address,\n","            \"nonce\": nonce,\n","            \"gas\": 400000,\n","            \"gasPrice\": gas_price\n","        })\n","\n","        # Firmar transacción\n","        signed_txn = w3.eth.account.sign_transaction(\n","            txn,\n","            private_key=PRIVATE_KEY\n","        )\n","\n","        # Enviar transacción\n","        tx_hash = w3.eth.send_raw_transaction(\n","            signed_txn.raw_transaction\n","        )\n","\n","        print(f\"⏳ Transacción enviada: {w3.to_hex(tx_hash)}\")\n","\n","        # Esperar confirmación\n","        receipt = w3.eth.wait_for_transaction_receipt(tx_hash, timeout=300)\n","\n","        if receipt.status == 1:\n","            print(f\"✅ Vehículo registrado en bloque: {receipt.blockNumber}\")\n","        else:\n","            print(\"⚠️ La transacción falló\")\n","\n","        return receipt\n","\n","    except Exception as e:\n","        print(f\"❌ Error al registrar vehículo: {e}\")"],"metadata":{"id":"jsWfJRVH2J-s","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1777091974096,"user_tz":300,"elapsed":47,"user":{"displayName":"wilson adrian iriarte contento","userId":"05634470763664888083"}}},"execution_count":50,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["# Registro de un vehículo (ejemplo)\n","\n","Se ejecuta la función definida previamente para registrar un vehículo en la blockchain.\n","\n","Este ejemplo simula la creación de un NFT que representa un automóvil con sus características básicas."],"metadata":{"id":"oq8gieGB2hlD"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["# Registrar un vehículo de prueba\n","registrar_vehiculo(\n","    \"VIN-001\",\n","    \"Toyota\",\n","    \"Corolla\",\n","    2022\n",")"],"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"IsevYJTI2QfX","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1777092023972,"user_tz":300,"elapsed":3726,"user":{"displayName":"wilson adrian iriarte contento","userId":"05634470763664888083"}},"outputId":"e052a83f-1716-47de-941d-eb15f737280b"},"execution_count":51,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["🚀 Registrando vehículo: VIN-001\n","⏳ Transacción enviada: 0xee46307b61c11dea994e6c77b92f5ddf4b0b31442d9dd9d293d7b45e7830a448\n","✅ Vehículo registrado en bloque: 10727346\n"]},{"output_type":"execute_result","data":{"text/plain":["AttributeDict({'type': 0,\n"," 'status': 1,\n"," 'cumulativeGasUsed': 6980791,\n"," 'logs': [],\n"," 'logsBloom': HexBytes(''),\n"," 'transactionHash': HexBytes('0xee46307b61c11dea994e6c77b92f5ddf4b0b31442d9dd9d293d7b45e7830a448'),\n"," 'transactionIndex': 45,\n"," 'blockHash': HexBytes('0x604a7993b7069a895be43690b1c6c9fd25486d16fbb8b2726dc8a9fb8858f287'),\n"," 'blockNumber': 10727346,\n"," 'gasUsed': 26150,\n"," 'effectiveGasPrice': 47836489,\n"," 'from': '0xF5f3f3e4A8c38E2CB9f5dD4415056dd3bC0531c6',\n"," 'to': '0xF5f3f3e4A8c38E2CB9f5dD4415056dd3bC0531c6',\n"," 'contractAddr